Effective Measure has released its website traffic statistics for June 2017, which show that News24 is the largest website in South Africa – with 6.4 million unique local browsers. Effective Measure is the official traffic measurement partner of the IAB South Africa and provides accurate traffic and demographics statistics for SA’s top websites. The table below shows the top websites in SA, based on local unique browsers. Only IAB-affiliated websites running Effective Measure’s tracking code are included. A comprehensive look at SA’s websites and their visitor numbers is available here: South African Internet Map. Effective Measure also tracks statistics for online publishers, showing the total reach of a publisher’s websites. The table below shows the top online publishers in South Africa, ranked according to local readership. The lists above do not include popular international websites like Google and Facebook. SimilarWeb provides a “top sites ranking” for South Africa, which shows the most popular websites among local Internet users.